    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with its signature high-pressure VANOS system and individual throttle bodies. This specimen retains its factory-correct Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, offering tactile engagement paired with a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is impeccable; the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the suspension geometry remains true with fresh bushings and factory dampers. Zero rod bearing issues or oil leaks. The exterior paint displays consistent depth and clarity, while the interior Nappa leather shows no bolster compression. A mechanically transparent, turn-key investment for the discerning enthusiast.",
