      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that defines the term 'mint condition.' This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its original deep-gloss factory finish without a single swirl mark or stone chip. The interior remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of wear, and the cabin still carries that distinct new-car scent. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documenting every fluid flush and inspection performed strictly ahead of schedule. Every button, switch, and sensor functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Includes both original master keys, the factory window sticker, and a custom-fit indoor car cover. This is a collector-grade vehicle for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
